1. For information regarding Veil Breakers Protocols, refer to section 23 of the Level 3 Employee Handbook.
2. A bipedal creature described as having an exposed skull, cervine antlers, and being in an early state of decay.
3. A large island on Lake Superior, north of the US state of Michigan.
4. A small island a short distance from Windigo Station.








                    

                                    





            
    

                    



                    
                        
                            
